		<div class="entry-meta">
			<span class="date"><a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/2018/03/05/13-52/" title="Permalink to 13 &#8211; 52" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2018-03-05T04:22:17+00:00">March 5, 2018</time></a></span><span class="categories-links"><a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/category/uncategorized/" rel="category tag">Uncategorized</a></span><span class="tags-links"><a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/akane/" rel="tag">Akane</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/apple/" rel="tag">Apple</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/avatar-01/" rel="tag">Avatar 01</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/ayuvesh/" rel="tag">Ayuvesh</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/emperor-sharidan/" rel="tag">Emperor Sharidan</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/hawthron/" rel="tag">Hawthron</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/milanda-darnassy/" rel="tag">Milanda Darnassy</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/mimosa/" rel="tag">Mimosa</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/professor-tellwyrn/" rel="tag">Professor Tellwyrn</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/shaeine/" rel="tag">Shaeine</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/teal/" rel="tag">Teal</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/the-jackal/" rel="tag">the Jackal</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/trissiny/" rel="tag">Trissiny</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/walker/" rel="tag">Walker</a></span><span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/author/webbonomicon/" title="View all posts by D. D. Webb" rel="author">D. D. Webb</a></span>					</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
