			<span class="date"><a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/2018/03/02/13-51/" title="Permalink to 13 &#8211; 51" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2018-03-02T02:39:40+00:00">March 2, 2018</time></a></span><span class="categories-links"><a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/category/uncategorized/" rel="category tag">Uncategorized</a></span><span class="tags-links"><a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/avei/" rel="tag">Avei</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/bishop-darling/" rel="tag">Bishop Darling</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/darius/" rel="tag">Darius</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/eserion/" rel="tag">Eserion</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/layla-sakhavenid/" rel="tag">Layla Sakhavenid</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/principia/" rel="tag">Principia</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/schwartz/" rel="tag">Schwartz</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/style/" rel="tag">Style</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/tallie/" rel="tag">Tallie</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/tricks/" rel="tag">Tricks</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/trissiny/" rel="tag">Trissiny</a></span><span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/author/webbonomicon/" title="View all posts by D. D. Webb" rel="author">D. D. Webb</a></span>					</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
