			<span class="date"><a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/2018/02/28/13-50/" title="Permalink to 13 &#8211; 50" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2018-02-28T05:46:58+00:00">February 28, 2018</time></a></span><span class="categories-links"><a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/category/uncategorized/" rel="category tag">Uncategorized</a></span><span class="tags-links"><a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/crystal/" rel="tag">Crystal</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/melaxyna/" rel="tag">Melaxyna</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/natchua/" rel="tag">Natchua</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/oak/" rel="tag">Oak</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/professor-tellwyrn/" rel="tag">Professor Tellwyrn</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/ravana/" rel="tag">Ravana</a></span><span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/author/webbonomicon/" title="View all posts by D. D. Webb" rel="author">D. D. Webb</a></span>					</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
