			<span class="date"><a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/2018/02/23/13-48/" title="Permalink to 13 &#8211; 48" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2018-02-23T07:22:47+00:00">February 23, 2018</time></a></span><span class="categories-links"><a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/category/uncategorized/" rel="category tag">Uncategorized</a></span><span class="tags-links"><a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/anjal/" rel="tag">Anjal</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/ayuvesh/" rel="tag">Ayuvesh</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/brother-arlund/" rel="tag">Brother Arlund</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/darius/" rel="tag">Darius</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/fross/" rel="tag">Fross</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/gabriel/" rel="tag">Gabriel</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/juniper/" rel="tag">Juniper</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/layla-sakhavenid/" rel="tag">Layla Sakhavenid</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/mandip/" rel="tag">Mandip</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/principia/" rel="tag">Principia</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/rajakhan/" rel="tag">Rajakhan</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/ruda/" rel="tag">Ruda</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/schwartz/" rel="tag">Schwartz</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/tallie/" rel="tag">Tallie</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/toby/" rel="tag">Toby</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/trissiny/" rel="tag">Trissiny</a>, <a href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/tag/vadrieny/" rel="tag">Vadrieny</a></span><span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="https://tiraas.wordpress.com/author/webbonomicon/" title="View all posts by D. D. Webb" rel="author">D. D. Webb</a></span>					</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
